fields.description:
h3. Steps to Reproduce
Fresh install of titanium studio produces no solutions.
Restoring 'Content Assist' in preferences/properties does not solve the solution either.
Others have cited they have had problems with this since the release of 3.2.0 as well.

h3. Actual Result
No content assist other than some of the main modules of the studio.  The stupid will offer assistance in inserting things like Ti.UI or Ti.App, and what not, but will have no content outside of that.

h3. Expected Result
A fully functional content assistant.

comments.body: This appears to be a known issue described at TISTUD-5989. Please let us know that module is not providing you the content assist functionality so that we can try to troubleshoot the issue.
